---
title: Crunchy Italian Chicken Sheet Pan Bake with Spiced Potatoes & Lemony Broccoli
description: Forget about that sous-vide machine you thought you might use some day, the full set of pots and pans you got for your new place, and all of the other gadgets taking up space in your kitchen cabinets: Everything in this recipe is prepared on a single baking sheet! Yep, all you have to do is pop it in the oven and wait for dinner to be ready. We’re talking Italian-spiced chicken, lemony broccoli, and spiced spuds. The best part (besides digging in)? Fewer pots and pans means quicker cleanup and more time to enjoy the meal. That’s a weeknight win.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/611d2327450c845128326347-a4854818.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/crunchy-italian-chicken-sheet-pan-bake-611d2327450c845128326347-919d77ba.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
cuisine: Italian
course: main course
author: Michelle Doll Olson
servings: 2
